vibesExplanation: The vibe of this workout predominantly aligns with 'The Meditative Grind' due to the focus on endurance and repetition inherent in rowing. Lastly, the upbeat pop music and interval format give it elements of 'The Rhythmic Powerhouse', where the beat of the music drives the workout, contributing to a score of 0.6.
